Welcome back to The Varsity, my twice-weekly private email on
the money, power, and influence that fuels the sports industrial complex. I=
 was sad to see this morning=E2=80=99s news about the death of Bob Uecker, =
who parlayed a journeyman baseball career into media stardom. Juuuuuuuust a=
 bit outside ( https://youtu.be/g_wc9JvTXGc?feature=3Dshared&t=3D47&utm_cam=
paign=3DThe+Varsity+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%281%2F16%2F25%29&utm_content=3DThe+Varsi=
