I knew there was something going on behind the scenes during the
Commanders-Titans game on December 1. Loyal readers will recall that Josh H=
arris, the principal owner of the Washington Commanders and one of the co-f=
ounders of Apollo Global Management, invited me and my two sons to enjoy th=
